---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title={"Who we are — International Rotary Fellowship of Healthcare Professionals"} description={"Healthcare Professionals united by the ideal of 'service above self'. We are a global family — the International Rotary Fellowship of Healthcare Professionals (IRFHP)."}>
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / About us</p>
    <h1>Who we are</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>Healthcare Professionals united by the ideal of &lsquo;service above self&rsquo;. We are a global family. Our full name is the International Rotary Fellowship of Healthcare Professionals (IRFHP)</p>

      <div class="two-col-img">
        <img src="/images/2024/07/Rotary_Fellowship_Healthcare_Proff_Bylaws_amended-pdf-724x1024.jpg" alt="Cover page of the IRFHP amended bylaws document">
        <img src="/images/2024/07/Homepage-main-photo.jpg" alt="Members of the Fellowship of Healthcare Professionals">
      </div>

      <h2>Our governance</h2>
      <p>We operate in compliance with the Rotary International&rsquo;s policies for Rotary Fellowships, but we are not be an agency of, or controlled by, Rotary International.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/images/2022/07/Rotary_Fellowship_Healthcare_Proff_Constit-2.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Our constitution</a></li>
        <li><a href="/images/2022/07/Trust-deed-signed-final-3.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Our Trust governing document</a></li>
        <li><a href="/images/2025/03/Rotary_Fellowship_Healthcare_Proff_Bylaws_amended2.docx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Our bylaws</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our policies</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/images/2024/12/Data-Protection-Policy_2024-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Data Protection</a></li>
        <li><a href="/images/2024/12/Risk-Management-Policy_2024.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Risk management</a></li>
        <li><a href="/images/2024/12/Equality-and-Diversity-Policy_2024.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Equality and Diversity</a></li>
        <li><a href="/images/2024/12/Dignity-Policy_2024.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dignity Policy</a></li>
        <li><a href="/images/2024/12/Anti-Fraud-and-Anti-Corruption-Policy_2024-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Anti-Fraud</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Branches</h2>
      <p>We recognises that in fulfilling our mission we must adopt a policy of &lsquo;global thinking and local action&rsquo;. We have three active branches</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Ukraine</li>
        <li>Egypt</li>
        <li>Uganda</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Subgroups</h2>
      <p>We&rsquo;ve two subgroups</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Health Outcomes and Patient Safety (HOPS)</li>
        <li>Safe and Sustainable Medical Equipment Supply (SASMES)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
